'''Yammal-jell''' was a creature once used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] as a [[biot]]. After the resolution of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], the yammal-jells resided in [[Liberation Lake]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], where they often served as the [[Hawk-bat/Legends|Hawk-bats]]' prey.

